Guess My Number Game

This is a single player game where the player tries to guess a randomly generated number between 1 and 20. The game will provide hints to the player after each guess, letting them know if their guess was too high or too low. The player can continue guessing until they correctly guess the number, at which point the game will end and the player will receive a congratulatory message.

How to Play
The game will generate a random number between 1 and 20.
The player will be prompted to enter their first guess.
The game will provide feedback to the player after each guess, letting them know if their guess was too high or too low.
The player can continue guessing until they correctly guess the number.
After the player correctly guesses the number, the game will end and the player will receive a congratulatory message.